/*Intuition :-
    Ekhane muloto question je kotha ta bola hoise ta holo 

    1) a[i]+a[j] should be divisable by x , 2) a[i]-a[j] should be divisable by y .

    Eitare bola jay je 

    1) (a[i]+a[j])%x = 0 ==> (a[i]%x + a[j]%x)%x = 0 ; 
    Er theke conclusion e ashte pari je hoy a[i] ar a[j] individually x er multiple,
    otherwise a[i]+a[j] er summation == x ;

    2) (a[i]-a[j])%y = 0 ==> a[i]%y = a[j]%y . 
    Er theke conclusion e ashte pari je hoy a[i] ar a[j] duita shoman jokhon modulo y .

    Ekhane ekta map of ll , map create kora hoise jekhane jeshokol value er jonno 
    val%x = something oi shokol value er jonno val%y er freq store kora hocche .
    ans er moddhe oi porjonto input newa value gulor sathe ekhon input newa current 
    value er pair toiri korar chesta kora hocche .

    Ekhane x er value tar jonno ektu modular arithmetic tricks khatanu hoise jekhane

    Negative value cover dewar style ta use hoise , jemon -2 % 5 er value calculation
    er system holo ((-2 % 5)+5)%5 = (-2+5)%5 = 3 .

    Thik ekivabe x er hishab ta hoise val % x to current value tai provide kortese . 
    Er shonge pair toiri korar jonne amader dorkar holo (x - (val%x))%x . 

    Tai frequency store kora hoise val%x er , ar call kora hoise er pair number er .

*/

void giveMeMyGloryBack() {
    ll n , x , y ; cin >> n >> x >> y ;
    map<ll,map<ll,ll>> mp ; ll ans = 0LL ;
    tamjid(n){
        ll val ; cin >> val ; ans += mp[(x-(val%x))%x][val%y] ;
        mp[val%x][val%y]++ ;
    }
    cout << ans << endl ;
}
